13. O-O{ This was played in the only game at the Grandmaster level between Roseneck-Tari. Instead of following the engine's top line and Tari's choice of ... Bf5 , I prefer the direct reply. }
13. f5{ Just look at our pawns and the centre! This looks much more intimidating and is quite fine objectively as well. We want to play ... Bd6  next, bringing back the bishop into the game. }
14. Ne5{ The only challenging try. White wants to push  f3  and attack our pawn on  f5 . }( 14.a3 { just helps us after }14...Bd6⩱ { . } )
