21. Qc7{ The last subtlety. We are ready to play  Ne5  next and have a comfortable game. All you need to remember is that you need to keep making threats,and put pressure on  b2  pawn along with the penetration of c-file. }( { Note that }21...Qc2 { the most logical, but runs into }22.Nd4 { allowing white to consolidate with  Be3  coming next. } )
22. Bf4
22. Qc2{ The difference here is that the  b2 -pawn is attacked. }
