11. exd5{ We are again renewing the threat of ... Qxa5 , and meeting  Nb3  with ... c4 . White has an extraordinary move. }
12. Bf4( { This is the crux of the operation that starts with  Na5 . The issue is that }12...Qxa5 { would run into }13.Bxd5 { , and we can't play }13...Ra7 { due to }{ . Nevertheless, we do have an appropriate response. } )
