( { In this chapter, we'll cover all of White's alternatives on move 7, excluding the main moves,   }7.Ne5 { & }7.Qc2 { , which we have already discussed. }7.Qa4 { appears to be the most critical sideline, preventing us from playing  ...b5 . In addition, Magnus has tried }7.Na3 { , making it somewhat important. } )1. d4
