24. Qf3{ we start bringing our pieces in with }
24. Qe7+{ Our king is misplaced, but so is the knight on  f7 . We have sufficient counterplay and will bring the  h8 -rook into the game next. A difficult line, but for both sides. White needs to know a lot of new stuff, which is not the case usually when they play the London system. }
