14. Bb5{ White guards te  b2 -pawn by blocking it with the bishop, simultaneously getting it out of the vulnerable square on  b5 . }
14. Nf4{ We continue to make threats. Our threat is not only  Nxg2 , but to meet  O-O  with  a6 , after which the  a6 -bishop is trapped. }
