9. O-O{ We finish our kingside development and look to play  c5  next. }
10. Rc1{ White brings the rook into the game and keeps an eye on the c-file. }
10. Re8{ We play the typical  Re8  to complete our kingside development and then aim to play either ... c5  or ... e5  next, depending on White's actions. }
